## المرحلة 6 — BloodRequestService (تعديل) 🟡

### 6.1 تعديل `BloodRequestService.cs`
- [x] تعديل `FulfillRequestAsync`:
  - [x] إضافة: `request.QuantityFulfilled += quantity`
  - [x] استبدال `request.Status = RequestStatus.Fulfilled` بـ:
    ```
    if (request.QuantityFulfilled >= request.QuantityNeeded)
        request.Status = RequestStatus.Fulfilled;
    else
        request.Status = RequestStatus.PartiallyFulfilled;
    ```
  - [x] تحقق `quantity > (request.QuantityNeeded - request.QuantityFulfilled)` بدلاً من `quantity > request.QuantityNeeded`

